quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  7,117,"Men wahyini e Muusaa wonnde : \"Bugo tuggordu maa ndun\". Jaka yoo hindi moЙ—a ko Й“e fefindotonoo"
  7,118,"Goonga on feeГұi, ko Й“e gollaynoo kon [fow] boni"
  7,119,ЖҒe foolaa Й—on Й“e hooti ko Й“e jaasuЙ“e
  7,120,MbileeЙ“e Й“en suuyi sujji
  7,121,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Men gomЙ—inii JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  7,122,JeyЙ—o Muusaa e Haaruuna
  7,123,"Fir'awna wi'i : \"On gomЙ—in mo ado mi duЕӢinannde=sakkitoore on? Pellet, Й—um Й—oo ko fewjoore nde fewjuЙ—on ka saare fii no yaltiniron ton yimЙ“e mayre. ma on anndonu"
  7,124,"Ma mi taЖҙa juuЙ—e mon Й—en e koyЙ—e mon Й—en (mi) luutindira, refti ma mi feta on denndaangal"
  7,125,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Menen, ko faade ka Joomi amen woni ruttorde amen"
  7,126,"A aГұiraali men si wanaa fii men gomЙ—inii Maandeeji Joomi amen, tuma nde Й—i arunoo men. Joomi amen! Yuppu muГұal e amen, Жҙettitaa men ko men jebbilii Й“e"
  7,127,"Mbatu yimЙ“e Fir'awna ngun wi'i : \"A accay Muusaa e yimЙ“e mun Й“en no bonnira ka leydi, o acce an e reweteeЙ—i maa Й—in?!\" O wi'i : \"Ma men waru Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e worЙ“e Й“en men accita Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e rewЙ“e Й“en (wuura). Pellet, menen, e dow maЙ“Й“e ko men foolooЙ“e"
  7,128,"Muusaa maakani yimЙ“e makko Й“en : \"Wallinoree Alla muГұГұoЙ—on. Pellet, leydi ndin ka Alla woodani, Himo ronina ndi on Mo O muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Battane moЖҙЖҙe Й—en ko gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en woodani"
  7,129,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Men lorranooma ado a arde men e Й“aawo nde arЙ—aa men\". O maaki : \"Hino jortaa nde Joomi mon halkata gaГұo mon O lontina on ka leydi, O ndaara ko honno gollirton"
  7,130,"GomЙ—ii Men nanngirii yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en kokke e Й—uytagol dimЙ—e ; belajo'o, Й“e waajitoto"
  7,131,"Si moЖҙЖҙere nden arii Й“e, Й“e wi'a : \"MeЙ—en hanndi e ndee Й—oo\" ; si bone on heЙ“ii Й“e, Й“e kiitinora Muusaa e wonnduЙ“e e makko Й“en. Anndee pellet, kiiti maЙ“Й“e Й—in ko ka Alla iwri, kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en anndaa"
  7,132,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Kala ko addan Й—aa Й“en e Aayaa fii no mbilЙ—oraa men Й—um ; men wonaali gomЙ—inooЙ“e ma"
  7,133,"Men wurti e maЙ“Й“e waame, e kanu, e karan=tendi, e totiiji=paabi, e ЖҙiiЖҙam, ko Aayeeje fensitaaЙ—e, Й“e mawnintinii, Й“e laatii yimЙ“e bomЙ“e"
  7,134,"Tuma nde lepte Й—en yanunoo e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'i : \"ko an Muusaa, torano men Joomi maa sabu kon ko O ahodi e maaЙ—a. Si a huncanii men Й—ee lepte, ma men gomЙ—ine, ma men accide kadi e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en"
  7,135,"Nde Men huncannoo Й“e lepte Й—en haa e lajal ngal Й“e yottotoo, jaka yoo kamЙ“e ko Й“e firtooЙ“e (ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin)"
  7,136,"Men yottii e maЙ“Й“e ; Men yooliri Й“e ka maayo sabu ko Й“e fenniri kon Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“e laatii welsindiiЙ“e e majje"
  7,137,"Men ronini yimЙ“e wonanooЙ“e lo'ineede Й“en fuЙ—naange leydi ndin e hiirnaange mayri ndi Men barkini e mu'un. Konngol Joomi maa moЖҙЖҙongol ngol timmii e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en sabu ko Й“e muГұГұinoo kon. Men halki ko Fir'awna e yimЙ“e mun Й“en moЖҙЖҙinanynoo, e kon ko Й“e Й“amtaynoo (e kuЙ“eeje)"
  7,138,"Men lummbini Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en maayo ngon, Й“e rewi ka yimЙ“e ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e (e rewugol) sanamuuji mu'un, Й“e wi'i : \"Ko an yo Muusaa, waЙ—an men reweteeЙ—o wano reweteeЙ—i woodirani Й“e non\". O maaki : \"Pellet, onon ko on yimЙ“e majjooЙ“e"
  7,139,"Pellet, Й“ee Й—oo, ko Й“e woni e mun kon ko halkaaЙ—um, kadi ko mere woni ko Й“e gollaynoo"
  7,140,"E ko ko woori Alla mi Й—aЙ“Й“anta on reweteeЙ—o, Kanko O Й“urnii on e Winndere nden"
  7,141,"(Annditee) tuma nde Men daЙ—ndunoo on e yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en, hiЙ“e meeЙ—ina on lepte bonЙ—e : Й“e wara Й“iЙ—Й“e mon worЙ“e Й“e heddina rewЙ“e mon Й“en. No e Й—um mooЙ—on jarrabuyee mawЙ—o immorde ka Joomi mon"